title: UK conference on Sudan fails to set up contact group for ceasefire talks
description: Major setback for diplomatic efforts to end two years of civil war as Arab states refuse to sign joint communiqueA British-led attempt to establish a contact group to facilitate ceasefire talks in Sudan fell apart on Tuesday when Arab states refused to sign a joint communique after a conference in London.The daylong argument between Egypt, Saudi Arabia and the United Arab Emirates over the communique represents a big diplomatic setback for efforts to end two years of civil war in Sudan. title: 'They’ve taken a hatchet': Joe Biden accuses Trump of wrecking social security in first major speech post-presidency
description: In his first public address since leaving office, former President Joe Biden accused Donald Trump of severely damaging the Social Security Administration. Speaking at a disability advocates' conference, Biden criticised the Trump administration's actions, including job cuts and new identity-verification rules. He alleged these measures aim to undermine the critical safety net to enable tax cuts for the wealthy.
author: TOI World Desk
